tab1.text1:
Hi and Welcome to our small but humble community!


I hope you like it here and enjoy your stay.


If you want to keep in touch with us or want any info regarding the server you got a Discord link right below





- Active ingame Admins right now=Krognet,Shaull


If you cant close out of this window try tabbing out of the game to free your mouse and then click the X
tab1.text2:
- Keep chat English/Swedish

- Be respectful to other users both here and on Discord

- Listen to mods

- Dont be a dick to people you dont know personally

- Dont be racist or, homophobic or sexist keep that to your friend group.

- If you see anything or notice anything dont hesitate to contact either 
  Krognet or Shaull on discord, there is a link below

- Please take down traps when you are done

- Dont block any caves or explorer notes


- WildDinoLvl=150

- Xp=2

- Harvest=3

- Taming=4

- BabyMature=14

- EggHatch=10

- StackSize=20
